---
import EvidenceField from './EvidenceField.astro';
---
<section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
  <EvidenceField />
  <div class="hero-copy">
    <p class="eyebrow">Kodaxa Innovations / Independent systems practice</p>
    <h1>Systems for<br />uncertain worlds<span>.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-lede">Trust infrastructure, agent governance, and instruments of clarity for environments where evidence matters.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a class="action-button" href="/work">Explore the work <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      <a class="text-link" href="#philosophy">Read the principles</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <aside class="hero-note" aria-label="Field note">
    <p class="section-label">Field note / 001</p>
    <blockquote>Decisions should carry their evidence with them.</blockquote>
    <p class="hero-note__meta">Proof-aligned systems / Human authority retained</p>
  </aside>
  <dl class="hero-ledger" aria-label="Practice record">
    <div><dt>Domain</dt><dd>Trust infrastructure</dd></div>
    <div><dt>Method</dt><dd>Evidence before action</dd></div>
    <div><dt>Current field</dt><dd>Programmable worlds</dd></div>
    <div><dt>Archive</dt><dd>Open systems record</dd></div>
  </dl>
</section>
